:"rH7xqd8Y28Cl"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["**Summary of insights**\n","\n","This dataset contains 32,561 individuals and 15 variables describing demographic and economic characteristics.\n","\n","The income distribution demonstrate that approximately **76%** of individuals earn 50K or less, on the other hand about **24%** earn more than 50K per year.\n","\n","The analysis of working hours shows that individuals earning more than **50K** work considerably more hours per week on average (approximately 45 hours) compared to those earning 50K or less (approximately 39 hours). The independent samples t-test confirmed that this difference is statistically significant (p < 0.001).\n","\n","Moreover, education level appears to be strongly associated with income. Individuals with higher education levels such as **Master's**,** Doctorate**, and **Professional School degrees** have a significantly higher probability of earning more than **50K** compared to **individuals** with lower education levels.\n","\n","In general, the results suggest that both **working hours** and **educational attainment** are important **factors** linked with higher income levels."],"metadata":{"id":"ZcIKA0NL38r4"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":[],"metadata":{"id":"fOFiwOLj6KJJ"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["#Saving cleaned dataset"],"metadata":{"id":"JNLYZGmq6LM5"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["## Excel/Pickle"],"metadata":{"id":"0aLL7YCR7--E"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["df_clean = df_raw.copy()\n","\n","save_path = \"/content/drive/MyDrive/Exploratory Data Analysis/Lab Task part 2/\"\n","\n","df_clean.to_excel(save_path + \"adult_income_cleaned.xlsx\", index=False)\n","df_clean.to_pickle(save_path + \"adult_income_cleaned.pkl\")"],"metadata":{"id":"fa-46WVT7gKv","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1772444634898,"user_tz":-60,"elapsed":12060,"user":{"displayName":"Maryam Asghar","userId":"08471015076485163553"}}},"execution_count":18,"outputs":[]}]}
